    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fall-front drawers often incorporated in bookcases or as the upper drawer in chests of drawers to provide a level surface convenient for writing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
